{"tid":161070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[苦悶生活]其實係咪得我先係咁？","createTime":"2017-03-18T09:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T09:12:02.000Z","uid":51004,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7482361ca61adfc587a19d16956d5f52c8f5a69e","tid":161070,"uid":51004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"小學嘅時候 開始接觸Online Game<br />\n每日放學返屋企 第一時間開電腦玩<br />\n玩到食飯都未肯收機 仲成日因為打機 而同家人嘈交<br />\n<br />\n去到中學 開始有飯錢 寧願食少啲<br />\n都要拎去買點數都試過<br />\n每日返學都同人傾打機 點樣去打副本<br />\n但去到dse 我知道唔可以再不停打機<br />\n每日操卷操卷操卷 考到全科合格 雖然係普遍人眼中呢啲成績係好差 但我已經好滿足<br />\n考完dse後 我忽然冇哂打機嘅意欲<br />\n入到Game 我覺得好無聊<br />\n來來去去都係禁禁禁 打打打<br />\n<br />\n直到而家出黎工作<br />\n不論係咩平台嘅Game 都唔岩我<br />\nPC Game,Online Game,PS4,手機<br />\n統統我都覺得好無聊<br />\n<br />\n最近成班同事食飯吹水 我先發現我竟然脫節哂<br />\n車 我唔識<br />\n機 我唔打<br />\n模型 我唔砌<br />\n高達 一集都未睇過<br />\n<br />\n唯一有小小興趣 就係整嘢食<br />\n有時間會整下cup cake,甜品,麵包等等<br />\n<br />\n每日都係返工放工訓教 好苦悶<br />\n有冇人比到啲意見我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f54ec0351cc3401ef837c720cd3ec90d350a1fe","tid":161070,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"每日都係返工放工訓教 好苦悶<br />\n<br />\nYES <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b60d6b4c747f8ae9271b412d345bc29d3e0ca8","tid":161070,"uid":